01:09:53,501 --> 01:09:55,541
- A heron looking up at the sky.
- Yes.

2234
01:09:56,041 --> 01:09:57,980
This is the place...

2235
01:09:57,981 --> 01:10:00,381
- where your hearts will race.
- Goodness.

2236
01:10:00,411 --> 01:10:02,510
This mission will be held on the vast sandy beach...

2237
01:10:02,511 --> 01:10:03,580
next to the blue sea.

2238
01:10:03,581 --> 01:10:05,850
- Yes.
- The Sea-entering Random Game.

2239
01:10:05,851 --> 01:10:07,020
- What?
- Sea-entering?

2240
01:10:07,021 --> 01:10:08,620
It's your moment, Jae Jun.

2241
01:10:08,621 --> 01:10:11,051
(He's flustered.)

2242
01:10:11,121 --> 01:10:12,991
It's your moment, Jae Jun.

2243
01:10:13,691 --> 01:10:15,661
(I want to enter the sea.)

2244
01:10:15,861 --> 01:10:18,161
(Jae Jun declared that he will enter the sea.)

2245
01:10:18,431 --> 01:10:20,831
It was warm earlier, but now I'm a bit cold.

2246
01:10:20,961 --> 01:10:22,170
I don't really want to go in now.

2247
01:10:22,171 --> 01:10:23,770
Do you remember?

2248
01:10:23,771 --> 01:10:25,491
"Stay in the cold water for three seconds."

2249
01:10:27,071 --> 01:10:28,687
"Stay in the cold water for three seconds."

2250
01:10:28,711 --> 01:10:30,841
"You'll get used to it. And that's life."

2251
01:10:31,011 --> 01:10:34,111
Don't we all have our own ways of living?

2252
01:10:34,381 --> 01:10:37,280
Why do we have to live according to his way?

2253
01:10:37,281 --> 01:10:38,381
That's right.

2254
01:10:38,551 --> 01:10:41,290
We'll have our 1st jump into the sea of 2026.

2255
01:10:41,291 --> 01:10:43,220
It's going to be cold today.

2256
01:10:43,221 --> 01:10:45,861
- It's a cold day.
- This will be held in teams, right?

2257
01:10:46,891 --> 01:10:48,661
It's really cold.

2258
01:10:48,891 --> 01:10:50,607
This mission, which decides who will enter the water,

2259
01:10:50,631 --> 01:10:52,161
will be held over three rounds.

2260
01:10:52,231 --> 01:10:54,160
The 1st team to secure 2 wins will win.

2261
01:10:54,161 --> 01:10:55,970
Okay. I think we should know...

2262
01:10:55,971 --> 01:10:57,500
- what game it is first.
- Yes.

2263
01:10:57,501 --> 01:10:59,571
- It's cold.
- Those are your vests.

2264
01:11:00,101 --> 01:11:01,841
Team Se Yoon gets the red vests.

2265
01:11:02,141 --> 01:11:04,040
- Okay.
- There'll be a separate one for me.

2266
01:11:04,041 --> 01:11:05,140
Here.

2267
01:11:05,141 --> 01:11:06,510
Will it fit Jae Jun?

2268
01:11:06,511 --> 01:11:08,281
- See if it fits, Jae Jun.
- What?

2269
01:11:08,611 --> 01:11:09,611
We'll hold them up.

2270
01:11:10,451 --> 01:11:11,691
- Should we put them on?
- Yes.

2271
01:11:12,021 --> 01:11:14,750
You came as Seon Ho, so the size is small.

2272
01:11:14,751 --> 01:11:16,751
That's right.

2273
01:11:17,321 --> 01:11:18,561
It's small.

2274
01:11:18,821 --> 01:11:20,621
Right. I can just wear it.

2275
01:11:21,191 --> 01:11:22,231
I'm Yoo Seon Ho.

2276
01:11:22,461 --> 01:11:23,461
Okay.

2277
01:11:23,462 --> 01:11:25,231
(It's tight.)

2278
01:11:25,531 --> 01:11:26,661
The wind is cold.

2279
01:11:27,031 --> 01:11:28,800
We would be doing something here.

2280
01:11:28,801 --> 01:11:30,371
It looks like it.

2281
01:11:30,671 --> 01:11:32,791
I guess these are our team colors. This is our stage.

2282
01:11:32,871 --> 01:11:35,770
Those who played games in the 2000s...

2283
01:11:35,771 --> 01:11:36,810
