2284
01:11:36,811 --> 01:11:38,640
Round One mission...

2285
01:11:38,641 --> 01:11:40,140
is Go Fight.

2286
01:11:40,141 --> 01:11:42,381
- Go Fight?
- What's this?

2287
01:11:42,951 --> 01:11:44,280
It's a match where you push all the members...

2288
01:11:44,281 --> 01:11:46,781
of the opposing team off the buoys.

2289
01:11:47,281 --> 01:11:50,951
(He was bad at games even then.)

2290
01:11:51,121 --> 01:11:53,160
You've done this on "X-man" before, right?

2291
01:11:53,161 --> 01:11:54,161
Yes.

2292
01:11:54,162 --> 01:11:56,191
Being fat doesn't guarantee winning.

2293
01:11:56,931 --> 01:11:58,330
Why does being fat...

2294
01:11:58,331 --> 01:12:00,400
- Why are you openly saying that?
- I'm sorry!

2295
01:12:00,401 --> 01:12:01,630
You're calling us fat.

2296
01:12:01,631 --> 01:12:03,070
- Who are you calling fat?
- I'm sorry.

2297
01:12:03,071 --> 01:12:04,130
I mean...

2298
01:12:04,131 --> 01:12:05,371
(Laughing)

2299
01:12:06,101 --> 01:12:09,140
Having a big build doesn't guarantee winning.

2300
01:12:09,141 --> 01:12:11,580
- He's hurting us.
- You're fat. He said it to you.

2301
01:12:11,581 --> 01:12:13,210
He said it to you.

2302
01:12:13,211 --> 01:12:15,151
- I'm sorry.
- So...

2303
01:12:15,411 --> 01:12:17,510
Round 1 is a best-of-3 match.

2304
01:12:17,511 --> 01:12:18,580
Okay.

2305
01:12:18,581 --> 01:12:20,950
We could sacrifice one person to win.

2306
01:12:20,951 --> 01:12:23,090
We could do that. But if the sacrifice doesn't work...

2307
01:12:23,091 --> 01:12:24,450
- That's right.
- Look at them.

2308
01:12:24,451 --> 01:12:26,491
- Right.
- This is the starting point?

2309
01:12:26,691 --> 01:12:28,631
It would be better if it were a 1-on-1 fight.

2310
01:12:29,131 --> 01:12:30,661
I'll take them all down.

2311
01:12:30,791 --> 01:12:32,430
Will you do that? Can you push all of them out?

2312
01:12:32,431 --> 01:12:34,231
Do we get on this and start?

2313
01:12:34,331 --> 01:12:36,830
Jae Jun learned judo.

2314
01:12:36,831 --> 01:12:39,040
- I'll do it.
- Can you push them all out?

2315
01:12:39,041 --> 01:12:40,270
I'll do it.

2316
01:12:40,271 --> 01:12:41,440
- He learned judo.
- From Department of Yongmudo...

2317
01:12:41,441 --> 01:12:42,611
of Yongin University.

2318
01:12:43,571 --> 01:12:45,511
This is just cute.

2319
01:12:45,841 --> 01:12:47,440
I feel safe.

2320
01:12:47,441 --> 01:12:48,451
(He is regarded as cute.)

2321
01:12:48,581 --> 01:12:50,381
Yunho is a tough opponent for me.

2322
01:12:50,951 --> 01:12:53,551
There should be someone who sacrifices himself.

2323
01:12:53,921 --> 01:12:55,691
When you two are holding on,

2324
01:12:56,091 --> 01:12:58,921
I'll run to the side and make a push.

2325
01:12:58,991 --> 01:13:00,620
- I think that's a good strategy.
- Right?

2326
01:13:00,621 --> 01:13:02,130
We have to decide on...

2327
01:13:02,131 --> 01:13:03,467
- who will head out first.
- Right.

2328
01:13:03,491 --> 01:13:05,500
Stay right there, everyone.

2329
01:13:05,501 --> 01:13:07,031
What? Should we rush in?

2330
01:13:07,761 --> 01:13:08,871
When should we go?

2331
01:13:09,171 --> 01:13:10,731
We'll start now!

2332
01:13:11,301 --> 01:13:12,441
The first match.

2333
01:13:13,341 --> 01:13:15,341
Let's take it slow as it's the first match.

2334
01:13:15,741 --> 01:13:16,810
Get ready.

2335
01:13:16,811 --> 01:13:18,531
(Which team will start by taking the lead?)

2336
01:13:19,011 --> 01:13:20,291
- Let's test each other.
- Gosh!

2337
01:13:21,911 --> 01:13:22,950
- Gosh!
- Hold on!

2338
01:13:22,951 --> 01:13:25,581
(To Jong Min who wanted to test each other, )

2339
01:13:26,281 --> 01:13:29,051
(he barges right at him as if he was about to swallow him.)

2340
01:13:29,321 --> 01:13:30,950
(Flustered)

2341
01:13:30,951 --> 01:13:31,991
Hold on!

2342
01:13:32,691 --> 01:13:34,891
(He gets pulled right away.)

2343
01:13:34,991 --> 01:13:36,590
(Floating)

2344
01:13:36,591 --> 01:13:37,591
Gosh!

2345
01:13:37,592 --> 01:13:39,901
(Watching from the front row seat)

2346
01:13:40,101 --> 01:13:41,571
(Pushing out)

2347
01:13:42,071 --> 01:13:44,631
- What was that?
- What was that?

2348
01:13:46,371 --> 01:13:49,441
(There's one person left now.)

2349
01:13:50,441 --> 01:13:53,281
(Jae Jun versus Yunho)

2350
01:13:53,511 --> 01:13:56,581
(Fatty Number 2 rushes at him right away.)

2351
01:13:56,881 --> 01:13:59,481
(Frightened)

2352
01:13:59,821 --> 01:14:02,851
(Jae Jun doesn't hesitate to attack him.)

2353
01:14:03,051 --> 01:14:06,591
(Will Jae Jun win against all three like this?)

2354
01:14:07,021 --> 01:14:08,191
He must be insane!

2355
01:14:08,761 --> 01:14:10,891
(His foot touches the ground!)

2356
01:14:12,431 --> 01:14:14,331
Hold on!

2357
01:14:14,431 --> 01:14:18,301
Show us your performance!

2358
01:14:18,671 --> 01:14:20,401
(A backflip)

2359
01:14:21,641 --> 01:14:22,671
Are you okay?

2360
01:14:23,011 --> 01:14:24,071
Show us your performance!

2361
01:14:26,781 --> 01:14:30,011
(Oh, time really flies.)

2362
01:14:30,751 --> 01:14:33,081
I thought a bull was rushing toward me for a second!

2363
01:14:33,681 --> 01:14:34,850
- Are you okay?
- I'm okay.

2364
01:14:34,851 --> 01:14:37,091
(Team Jae Jun takes the first match thanks to the bull.)

2365
01:14:37,291 --> 01:14:39,491
- It's stress-relieving. I'm okay.
- Hey!

2366
01:14:39,791 --> 01:14:42,361
- Take a deep breath.
- Gosh.

2367
01:14:43,261 --> 01:14:46,831
(He's about to hyperventilate.)

2368
01:14:47,001 --> 01:14:48,530
(Team Yunho is in trouble.)

2369
01:14:48,531 --> 01:14:49,731
You stay in the middle.

2370
01:14:49,931 --> 01:14:52,641
We'll hold you from behind. Just fight back.

2371
01:14:53,041 --> 01:14:54,500
If the three of us aren't together,

2372
01:14:54,501 --> 01:14:56,181
